Written and so now we have Payroll menu completed options in menu order for :-

A - Date Entry              - py000
H - Print Payment Register  - pyrgstr [ temp prog name ]
I - Account Entry           - py920
J - Deduction/Earning Entry - py900
K - History Entry           - py930
L - Employee Data Entry     - py010
R - Print Yearly 940 Report - print940 [ temp prog name ]
T - Print Employee Report   - empprint [ temp prog name ]
U - Print History Report    - hisprint [ temp prog name ]
V - Print Vacation Report   - vacprint [ temp prog name ]
W - Print Account List      - py920 option 2 ( of 2)
Y - Payroll Parameter Entry - py900
Z - ACAS System Setup       - sy002 - Existing program.

Options M and N removed as data entry is in py010 via a sub menu.

