So as of today coded programs are :

payroll	 - Main menu for Payroll.

py000	 - Date entry - allows change of todays date.

py010	 - Employee data entry four screens containing :
           1. Primary Data entry included name & address etc.
           2. Earn/Ded & Cost entry.
           3. Rate Data entry.
           4. Employee History entry.
           The last one to record payments of new employee from last employer
           for current year.

py900	 - Company data entry:
	       1. Company ID and general data.
	       2. Pay Intervals and Default Employee Payroll Data.
           3. Payroll System Configuration and GL Interface.
           4. Standard Deduction Rates.
           5. Federal Withholding Tax Table Entry.
           6. System Earning and Deduction Information

py920    - Account Table maintenance.

py930    - Employee History maintenance.

empprint - Employee report
hisprint - Emp History report
print940 - EoY 940 Report
pyrgstr  - Payment Register report
vacprint - Vacation report

 To be reviewed or done :
py9nn    - Tax table data entry per state, local and Federal by current and next year.



