These program name / numbers are subject to change and more than likely will be.
Some may be merged together.

The py100 series will be for reports of all types mostly with py100 acting as menu.
py110 and onwards for each report type including 940, 941 and W-2 reports.

py0nn  series for handling the primary processing with py010 written more or less.

py20 +  to process the main payroll apply processes and pay data entry steps.

The copy books stored in folder copybooks are subject to changes where some field
formats were guessed at and closer examination of the basic code as well as new
Cobol code reveals some more changes as new coding is added.

Update the payroll manual in folder ACAS-Manuals which is 1.0 or v1.0C for the
Cobol version.

The ones ending in 1.0B are for the CBasic version only which is stored within
Basic-Code folder.

